import React, {useState} from "react";
import { Form, Row, Col } from "react-bootstrap";

function PlayerField({ stt, data, setData }) {
    const [playerData, setPlayerData] = useState({
        playerName: "",
        dayOfBirth: Date,
        playerType: String,
        playerNote: String,
        numberOfGoals: Number,
        numberOfAssits: Number
    })
    
    return (
        <Row>
            <Col sm={1}>
                <Form.Group className="mb-3" style={{ textAlign: "center" }}>
                    {stt}
                </Form.Group>
            </Col>
            <Col sm={3}>
                <Form.Group className="mb-3">
                    <Form.Control type="text" value={playerData.playerName}/>
                </Form.Group>
            </Col>
            <Col sm={2}>
                <Form.Group className="mb-3">
                    <Form.Control type="date" />
                </Form.Group>
            </Col>
            <Col sm={3}>
                <Form.Group className="mb-3">
                    <Form.Control type="text" />
                </Form.Group>
            </Col>
            <Col sm={3}>
                <Form.Group className="mb-3">
                    <Form.Control type="text" />
                </Form.Group>
            </Col>
        </Row>
    );
}

export default PlayerField;
